Adalat – Legal Awareness and Access Platform
Adalat is a digital platform that helps people understand the Indian legal system. It provides easy access to information about legal rights, articles of the Constitution, criminal laws, and personal laws. Users can find verified lawyers (via government sources), nearby NGOs offering legal aid—especially for women—and share their experiences through a blog system.

To overcome language barriers, Adalat integrates the powerful Bhashini API, enabling support for multiple Indian languages and making legal resources accessible to all
